buela de la Plaza de Mayo que busca a su nieta son los motivos que la llevan a replantearse \"la historia oficial\".  /// ORIGINAL AUDIO SPANISH DOLBY DIGITAL 2.0 AND 5.1  ///  SUBTITLE: PORTUGUESE, SPANISH, ENGLISH/// GOT 26 WINS AND 8 NOMINATIONS / ACADEMY AWARDS, USA 1986, Won Oscar Best Foreign Language Film (Argentina), Nominated Oscar	Best Writing, Screenplay Written Directly for the Screen Luis Puenzo, Aída Bortnik /// GOLDEN GLOBES, USA 1986, Won Golden Globe Best Foreign Film Argentina./// Argentinean Film Critics Association Awards 1986, Won Silver Condor Best Film, Best Actress Norma Aleandro, Best Supporting Actor Patricio Contreras, Best Supporting Actress Chela Ruíz, Best New Actress Analia Castro, Best Director Luis Puenzo, Best Screenplay, Original Aída Bortnik, Luis Puenzo, Best Cinematography Félix Monti, Best Editing Juan Carlos Macías /// Berlin International Film Festival</Content><IsLinkSuppressed>0</IsLinkSuppressed></EditorialReview></EditorialReviews><BrowseNodes><BrowseNode><BrowseNodeId>2649512011</BrowseNodeId><Name>Movies</Name><Ancestors><BrowseNode><BrowseNodeId>2625374011</BrowseNodeId><Name>Departments</Name><IsCategoryRoot>1</IsCategoryRoot><Ancestors><BrowseNode><BrowseNodeId>2625373011</BrowseNodeId><Name>Movies &amp; TV</Name></BrowseNode></Ancestors></BrowseNode></Ancestors></BrowseNode><BrowseNode><BrowseNodeId>919296</BrowseNodeId><Name>Special Editions</Name><Ancestors><BrowseNode><BrowseNodeId>295214</BrowseNodeId><Name>Fully Loaded DVDs</Name><Ancestors><BrowseNode><BrowseNodeId>2998369011</BrowseNodeId><Name>DVD Custom Stores</Name><Ancestors><BrowseNode><BrowseNodeId>2644982011</BrowseNodeId><Name>Custom Stores</Name><Ancestors><BrowseNode><BrowseNodeId>2644981011</BrowseNodeId><Name>Specialty Stores</Name><Ancestors><BrowseNode><BrowseNodeId>2625373011</BrowseNodeId><Name>Movies &amp; TV</Name></BrowseNode></Ancestors></BrowseNode></Ancestors></BrowseNode></Ancestors></BrowseNode></Ancestors></BrowseNode></Ancestors></Br